summary:
Hi, thanks for reaching out to me!

Who am I? Paul is a ‘quick and easy connector' as well as a salesman. An entrepreneur who is experienced in creating added value in networking for others. And always on the lookout for new opportunities.

He has over 14 years of internet experience and is a enthusiast with a passion for delivering profitable online services concerning:

✓ Webhosting
✓ Webdevelopment
✓ Lead generation
✓ Interim Management

Paul loves to work with professionals and has commercial awareness, drive and the focus on achieving objectives. In his spare time he loves playing with his two kids.

Specialties: Internet, Search Marketing, Online Marketing, Search Engine Marketing, SEM, Search Engine Optimization, SEO, Google, Search Engine Rankings, Funnels, SEO Consultant, Account Management, Acquisition, Sales, Organising, B2B, eBusiness, Resultdriven, Lead Generation,  Project Management, Communications, Webshops

» Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions!

awards:
[{'title': 'Sailed the ARC+ 2015: from Gran Canaria to St. Lucia via Cape Verde', 'description': "The ARC+ event attracts over 200 boats and 1.200 people every year, to sail almost 3.000 Nautical Miles across the Atlantic from Las Palmas to Saint Lucia with a stopover at Mindelo, Cape Verde islands. 

We participated in the Cruising Division with an X-Yachts 60 ft Monohull, winning first prize for Class A and coming first overall. The 'Nix' performed well throughout the first passage from Gran Canaria to São Vicente in an elapsed time of 4d 23h 13m 42s. 

In the second leg we sailed across the ARC+ finish line in an elapsed time of 10d 4h 51m 18s, winning Class A and took Line Honours for leading the ARC+ fleet into wonderful Saint Lucia on November 28th. Again a fast and successful passage for the 'Nix'. 

A great taste of ocean sailing, truly spectacular!

Read more: http://www.worldcruising.com/", 'issuer': 'World Cruising Club', 'date': {'month': 11, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}}]
